<WebGLProgram>
<summary>
The <strong><c>WebGLProgram</c></strong> is part of the <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API">WebGL API</see> and is a combination of two compiled <see cref="WebGLShader"/>s consisting of a vertex shader and a fragment shader (both written in GLSL).
</summary>
<remarks>
<para></para><para>To create a <c>WebGLProgram</c>, call the GL context's <see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.CreateProgram"/> function. After attaching the shader programs using <see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.AttachShader"/>, you link them into a usable program. This is shown in the code below.</para><para>See <see cref="WebGLShader"/> for information on creating the <c>vertexShader</c> and <c>fragmentShader</c> in the above example.</para>
<para>-<see cref="WebGLShader"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.AttachShader"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.CompileShader"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.CreateProgram"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.CreateShader"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.DeleteProgram"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.DeleteShader"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.DetachShader"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.GetAttachedShaders"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.GetProgramParameter"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.GetProgramInfoLog"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.GetShaderParameter"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.GetShaderPrecisionFormat"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.GetShaderInfoLog"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.GetShaderSource"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.IsProgram"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.IsShader"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.LinkProgram"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.ShaderSource"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.UseProgram"/><br/>-<see cref="WebGLRenderingContext.ValidateProgram"/><br/></para>
<para><seealso href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLProgram"> <em>See also on MDN</em> </seealso></para>
</remarks>
</WebGLProgram>
